data.description: Discover a magnificent lifestyle in this exquisite 5-bedroom, 3-bath estate on over.25 acres. A dream for car enthusiasts with a 3-car garage, this home boasts elegance and functionality. The open floor plan, illuminated by recessed lighting and 10-foot doors, seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and family rooms, creating a perfect space for entertaining. The gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances, 42-inch cabinets with crown molding, granite countertops, and a large island. Double sliding patio doors lead to a screened patio with a breathtaking view of the pond. The owner's suite is a sanctuary with a spa-like bathroom, a double sink, and two walk-in closets. With 12-foot ceilings, an irrigation system, and an entertainment connection for patio surround sound, this home is a true masterpiece of comfort and style. Welcome home to luxury and tranquility.
